The Essence of Balayage: A Timeless Technique
Balayage, derived from the French word meaning "to sweep," embodies a freehand hair coloring technique that creates natural, sun-kissed highlights with seamless blending. Unlike traditional foiling methods, balayage delivers a softer, more organic look, enhancing your hair's dimension and movement. At Code Hair, we elevate this technique to an art form, using precision and creativity to tailor each balayage application to suit your individual features and personality.

Why Choose Balayage?
Natural Results: Achieve effortlessly chic hair with subtle transitions and soft gradients.
Low Maintenance: Enjoy longer intervals between touch-ups, as balayage grows out gracefully without harsh regrowth lines.
Versatility: Whether you desire subtle highlights or bold contrasts, balayage offers endless possibilities to customize your look.
Enhanced Texture: Elevate your hair's texture and depth with multidimensional color effects.
